post_text: Riata Bultje and Cole Bergin represented Andes Central FFA on Thursday at the State Fair. Riata participated in the breeding sheep show with her Rambouillet yearling ewe and a January ewe lamb, as well as showmanship. Cole participated in the market sheep show with his crossbred ewe lamb. Great job Riata & Cole!
